-- Mexico’s Calderon Congratulates Vazquez Mota on Primary Win
-- B y   B e n   B a i n
-- 2012-02-06T03:20:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-06/mexico-s-calderon-congratulates-vazquez-mota-on-primary-win.html
Josefina Vazquez Mota was
congratulated by Mexican President Felipe Calderon after winning
his party’s nomination for the presidency, the leader’s office
said in an e-mailed statement.  Vazquez Mota, 51, is leading the preliminary results with
55 percent of the vote, Jose Espina, the  National Action Party ’s
chief election coordinator, told reporters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Bain in Mexico City at 
